586
00:36:41,320 --> 00:36:42,520
That's not even the same one.

587
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:46,120
Boss, why are you worrying about this?

588
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:48,400
I watched you grow up, didn't I?

589
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,640
Time you got yourself a girl.

590
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:53,640
You worry more than my own dad.

591
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:00,360
Eat while it's hot.

592
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:05,120
Have some tripe.

593
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:05,840
Seven seconds.

594
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,120
I'll do it.

595
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,520
Skip the One of Characters.

596
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:16,600
Oh, my goodness!

597
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,160
Six of Bamboo.

598
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:20,960
My draw.

599
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:23,360
Four of Bamboo.

600
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:28,280
Nine of Bamboo.

601
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:29,960
Mahjong!

602
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:31,520
Seven pairs.

603
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:34,400
Nice luck, huh?

604
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:36,080
Your luck's crazy good today.

605
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,040
Right?

606
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:38,120
That's it, I'm done.

607
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,080
I'm heading home.

608
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,640
My mom's probably awake.

609
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:41,760
Gotta help her to the toilet.

610
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:43,600
Done for now, next time, next time.

611
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:44,200
Sister Lan.

612
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:46,480
Did somebody bless those hands of yours?

613
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:47,640
Wouldn't even let me have a smoke.

614
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:48,360
Come on.

615
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,400
We need a fourth, let's keep going.

616
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:50,360
How can we play like this?

617
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,960
Done, we're done.

618
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:52,760
Listen to me.

619
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,760
That old Chen,

620
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,280
got another job.

621
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:56,040
I can't go.

622
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:57,800
Go get yourself ready in a bit and take it.

623
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:58,520
Perfect timing.

624
00:37:58,520 --> 00:37:59,920
It'll cover that hole of Yiran's.

625
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,560
What hole of Yiran's?

626
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:05,560
We already heard about it.

627
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:08,440
Didn't you dress up as a bear and scare a kid?

628
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:10,840
And they're making you two

629
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,160
pay two hundred thousand.

630
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:14,200
That's blatant extortion, isn't it?

631
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:17,760
If you need money, just tell me.

632
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,920
I've got some savings.

633
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:27,080
That damn kid never told me.

634
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,160
Are you out of your mind?

635
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:49,880
What's the deal?

636
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,800
What's gotten into you?

637
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:59,880
You do still love your mom, don't you?

638
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:03,880
Wu Huilan.

639
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:07,080
Quit watching those trashy soap operas.

640
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:10,680
You scared the hell out of me.

641
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:15,560
Are you paying off a debt?

642
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,440
What debt?

643
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,400
Auntie Juan told me all about it.

644
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:28,880
That damn son of a bitch.

645
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:30,160
She actually extorted money from us.

646
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,760
Demanding 200,000, greedy as hell.

647
00:39:31,760 --> 00:39:33,080
Is she even human?

648
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,840
Where would I get 200,000?

649
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:37,320
Don't listen to Auntie Juan's nonsense.

650
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:46,720
Those puppy-dog eyes of yours.

651
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:48,080
They can't fool me.

652
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,280
Fine.

653
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:57,960
I admit there really is something to it.

654
00:39:58,720 --> 00:40:01,200
But first, the reason I didn't tell you

655
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,200
is I was afraid you'd go pick a fight.

656
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:04,400
That's the only reason.

657
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:05,960
And another thing.

658
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,160
You don't have a job right now,

659
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:07,760
and no income either.

660
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:08,960
What could you do even if you knew?

661
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,040
Do you have money to pay?

662
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:16,800
You really underestimate me.

663
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,760
The money in this savings book

664
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:42,040
is what I saved up working in prison

665
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:44,280
I didn't spend a single cent all these years

666
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:47,560
And this too

667
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,880
Your dad gave me this when we got married

668
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,840
Take it and sell it

669
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,400
Pay off that debt right away

670
00:41:25,680 --> 00:41:26,480
Lijuan

671
00:41:27,560 --> 00:41:29,520
I took that job Old Chen mentioned

672
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:31,680
If you've got any more work

673
00:41:31,680 --> 00:41:32,720
just call me in on it too

674
00:41:33,320 --> 00:41:34,960
I really need the money these days

675
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,320
I'm sorry, Yiran

676
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,240
I honestly didn't know

677
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:46,640
You didn't tell Sister Lan

678
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:47,760
Auntie Juan, just tell me

679
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:48,840
How did you find out?

680
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:50,520
Yangyang told me

681
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:54,480
I can control the wind

682
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:55,960
Yangyang

683
00:41:56,160 --> 00:41:58,320
Tell Sister Yiran how you knew

684
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:01,360
I'm not telling you

685
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,200
I'm not telling you

686
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:04,400
Not telling me, huh?

687
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:04,920
Not telling me?

688
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:05,920
Then I'll unplug your fan

689
00:42:09,040 --> 00:42:10,000
Mommy

690
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:11,760
You little brat

691
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:12,920
When I say talk, you talk

692
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:18,840
Xiaojie told me while we were playing

693
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,920
My grandma told me

694
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,800
Director Ma told me

695
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,640
Chen Jianguo told me, that's who

696
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:31,440
My son Chen Baixi told me

697
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:33,000
Chen Baixi

698
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:33,840
Get out here right now

699
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:36,200
Come here

700
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,880
That mouth of yours

701
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,720
leaks like a cracked teapot

702
00:42:40,720 --> 00:42:41,360
No way

703
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:43,400
My lips are sealed tight as a lock

704
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:44,600
Last night

705
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:46,280
Wu Huilan found out about our debt deal

706
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:47,400
I asked a whole bunch of people

707
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:48,600
and it all came back to you

708
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,040
I just remembered

709
00:42:50,040 --> 00:42:50,760
maybe a few days ago

710
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,960
when Director Ma was talking with my dad

711
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:53,080
it slipped out

712
00:42:55,640 --> 00:42:56,200
Fine

713
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:56,840
My fault

714
00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:00,160
This Director Ma, honestly

715
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,240
but you're still the main culprit

716
00:43:07,680 --> 00:43:10,160
And I know all your secrets too

717
00:43:10,560 --> 00:43:11,760
What secrets of mine?

718
00:43:12,360 --> 00:43:13,120
Go sit over there

719
00:43:23,680 --> 00:43:24,480
Out with it.

720
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:26,520
What do you know?

721
00:43:26,880 --> 00:43:29,880
You let it slip that day at Wu Yuanfeng's place.

722
00:43:30,680 --> 00:43:32,040
I did feel something was off about him.

723
00:43:32,040 --> 00:43:33,080
But I didn't think much of it.

724
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:34,360
I could have stopped him.

725
00:43:34,360 --> 00:43:34,880
But I didn't.

726
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:35,320
I...

727
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:37,080
It's not like you can predict the future.

728
00:43:37,600 --> 00:43:38,920
How do you know I can't?

729
00:43:39,640 --> 00:43:40,640
Anyone else...

730
00:43:40,680 --> 00:43:43,360
would just laugh it off and forget it.

731
00:43:44,280 --> 00:43:45,560
But I studied art.

732
00:43:45,560 --> 00:43:47,200
My mind works differently from others.

733
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:49,320
So just come clean.

734
00:43:49,960 --> 00:43:51,760
Are you really like those people in movies?

735
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:53,000
Do you have some kind of superpower?

736
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:58,200
Some things...

737
00:43:58,680 --> 00:44:00,320
you're better off not knowing.

738
00:44:01,160 --> 00:44:02,400
Curiosity killed the cat.

739
00:44:02,400 --> 00:44:04,960
I'm afraid you couldn't handle the truth.

740
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:06,960
The world is vast.

741
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,040
Full of strange things.

742
00:44:08,040 --> 00:44:09,200
As long as you dare to say it,

743
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:10,800
I dare to believe it.

744
00:44:12,640 --> 00:44:13,440
Fine.

745
00:44:13,840 --> 00:44:15,040
If I tell you,

746
00:44:16,200 --> 00:44:18,760
you have to keep it a total secret.

747
00:44:18,760 --> 00:44:20,960
Don't go leaking like a cracked teapot again.

748
00:44:22,600 --> 00:44:23,480
I promise.

749
00:44:24,240 --> 00:44:25,480
If I break my word,

750
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:27,200
may lightning strike me down.

751
00:44:33,280 --> 00:44:33,960
Come on.

752
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:45,200
Come on, come on.

753
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:47,760
Come on.

754
00:44:48,320 --> 00:44:49,680
Come on.
